Myth Buster: The new coronavirus CANNOT be transmitted through mosquito bites.
To date there has been no information nor evidence to suggest that the new coronavirus could be transmitted by mosquitoes. 
Visit us https://t.co/7pQNfmLWSn
#quarantine #stayhome #staysafe #covid19 https://t.co/HHTt5ZltzD
